<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PolyChat Chats</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
  <script>
    const INITIAL_DATA = {
        
        message: "<%= message %>", 
        model:   "<%= model %>"
    };

    console.log("Data received from Backend:", INITIAL_DATA);
  </script>
<body>
    <div class="app-container">
        <aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-top">
                <div class="logo">
                    <svg class="icon-navy" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.456 2.456zM16.894 20.567L16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 001.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 001.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423 1.423z" />
                    </svg>
                    PolyChat
                </div>
                <button class="new-chat-btn"><span>+</span> New Chat</button>
            </div>
            
            <nav class="chat-history">
                <div class="history-item">Quantum computing encrypt...</div>
                <div class="history-item">React performance optimizat...</div>
                <div class="history-item active">Q3 Marketing Strategy</div>
                <div class="history-item">Python async best practices</div>
                <div class="history-item">Design system components</div>
            </nav>

            <div class="sidebar-bottom">
                <div class="footer-link">
                    <svg class="icon-small" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.343 3.94c.09-.542.56-.94 1.11-.94h1.094c.55 0 1.02.398 1.11.94l.149.894c.07.424.384.764.78.93.398.164.855.142 1.205-.108l.737-.527a1.125 1.125 0 011.45.12l.773.774a1.125 1.125 0 01.12 1.45l-.527.737c-.25.35-.272.806-.107 1.204.165.397.505.71.93.78l.894.15c.542.09.94.56.94 1.109v1.094c0 .55-.398 1.02-.94 1.11l-.894.149c-.424.07-.764.383-.93.78-.165.398-.143.854.107 1.204l.527.738a1.125 1.125 0 01-.12 1.45l-.773.773a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.45.12l-.737-.527c-.35-.25-.806-.272-1.203-.107-.397.165-.71.505-.781.929l-.149.894c-.09.542-.56.94-1.11.94h-1.094c-.55 0-1.019-.398-1.11-.94l-.148-.894c-.071-.424-.384-.764-.781-.93-.398-.164-.854-.142-1.204.108l-.738.527a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.45-.12l-.773-.774a1.125 1.125 0 01-.12-1.45l.527-.737c.25-.35.273-.806.108-1.204-.165-.397-.505-.71-.93-.78l-.894-.15c-.542-.09-.94-.56-.94-1.109v-1.094c0-.55.398-1.02.94-1.11l.894-.149c.424-.07.765-.383.93-.78.165-.398.143-.854-.108-1.204l-.526-.738a1.125 1.125 0 01.12-1.45l.773-.773a1.125 1.125 0 011.45-.12l.737.527c.35.25.807.272 1.204.107.397-.165.71-.505.78-.929l.15-.894z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
                    Settings
                </div>
                <div class="user-card">
                    <div class="user-avatar">AC</div>
                    <div class="user-meta">
                        <div class="user-name">Alex Chen</div>
                        <div class="user-plan">Pro Plan</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main class="content-area">
            <button class="sidebar-toggle" id="sidebarToggle">
                <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6.75h16.5M3.75 12h16.5m-16.5 5.25h16.5" />
                </svg>
            </button>

            <div class="scroll-wrapper" id = "chat-history-container">
                <header class="chat-header">
                    <h1><%=message%></h1>
                    <div class="model-info">
                        <svg class="icon-small" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 3v1.5M4.5 8.25H3m18 0h-1.5M8.25 19.5V21M12 3v1.5m0 15V21m3.75-18v1.5m0 15V21m-9-1.5h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75A2.25 2.25 0 004.5 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25zm.75-12h9v9h-9v-9z" /></svg>
                        Answer generated by <%= model%>
                        <div class="header-tools">
                            <svg class="tool-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 17.25v3.375c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-9.75a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V7.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H6.75a9.06 9.06 0 011.5.124m7.5 10.376h3.375c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25c0-4.46-3.243-8.161-7.5-8.876a9.06 9.06 0 00-1.5-.124H9.375c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v3.5m7.5 10.375H9.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125v-9.25m12 6.625v-1.875a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H9.75" /></svg>
                            <svg class="tool-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99" /></svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </header>

                <article class="chat-text">
                    <!-- <p>Quantum computing represents a paradigm shift in computational power that threatens the security foundations of the modern internet. Its impact on encryption is primarily categorized into two areas: <strong>Symmetric Encryption</strong> and <strong>Asymmetric (Public-Key) Encryption</strong>.</p>
                    
